{"word":"G670 - ἀποφορτίζομαι - apophortízomai - ap-of-or-tid'-zom-ahee - Unlade","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀποφορτίζομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">apophortízomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ap-of-or-tid'-zom-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Unlade</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - இறக்கு"},{"paragraph":"to disburden oneself to lay down a load, unlade, discharge"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G575 - ἀπό - apó - apo'/575\">G575</a> and the middle voice of <a href=\"#/G5412 - φορτίζω - phortízō - for-tid'-zo/5412\">G5412</a>; to <i>unload:</i> - unlade.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}